[Student "S"]
{There is only one reason that NORTH should not overcall with 1\S. He is too strong. 
The maximum strength of an overcall is 16 points. Above that you should double.

So NORTH doubles, and after SOUTH bids 2\C, NORTH bids 2\S. This shows an overcall 
type hand, but with 17 or more points.

SOUTH has fine trump support and 8 points so she bids a confident 4\S.}

